{"id":"entities/jacob-cocheu","title":"Jacob Cocheu","type":"entities","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. ONID <code>cocheuj</code>. <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/osu\">OSU</a> <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/cs-461\">CS 461</a> capstone teammate (Group 27) on the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/baby-tracking-app\">privacy friendly baby tracking app</a>. First mentioned <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-12-04-requirements-document-2\">PRD</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Connections: <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/osu\">osu</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/cs-461\">cs 461</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/bryant-shitabata\">bryant shitabata</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/sonny-box\">sonny box</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/baby-tracking-app\">baby tracking app</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"entities/bryant-shitabata","label":"Bryant Shitabata"},{"id":"entities/cs-461","label":"CS 461 (OSU Software Engineering capstone)"},{"id":"summaries/2024-12-04-requirements-document-2","label":"CS 461 Privacy-Friendly Baby Tracking App PRD (12/4/24)"},{"id":"entities/osu","label":"Oregon State University (OSU)"},{"id":"projects/baby-tracking-app","label":"Privacy-Friendly Baby Tracking App (CS 461 capstone)"},{"id":"entities/sonny-box","label":"Sonny Box"}]}
